The '''Children's Museum''' was a [[Museum/Legends|museum]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], built [[200 BBY/Legends|circa 200 BBY]]. It chronicled the impact that young people had on [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

Explorer [[Brin Hesk'l]] once claimed that he discovered a trigger mechanism on the floor of the museum, which opened a secret room where important documents were stored.

